l've given over, like, 60 lectures on the cultivation of plants.

246
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:26,250
我的论文刊登在杂志上 我也出书
l'm a published author, both in magazine and book form.

247
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:28,790
我对兰花已经了若指掌...
And l have extensive experience with orchids...

248
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:34,330
