...and the asexual micropropagation of orchids under aseptic cultures.

249
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:39,430
那是实验室的工作 和你的苗圃完全不一样
That's laboratory work. lt's not at all like your nursery work.

250
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:42,770
我简直是天资异秉无人可及
l'm probably the smartest person l know.

251
00:15:43,370 --> 00:15:45,600
- 谢谢你 - 甭客气
- Thank you. - You're very welcome.

